incidents.name: Issues for Families and Securities using Cloudflare's public resolver via DoH and DoT

incident_updates.body: DoH and DoT services have been fully restored.
A fix has been implemented and we are monitoring the results.

The IPv6 addresses for the Families (2606:4700:4700::1003, 2606:4700:4700::1113) public resolvers via DoH have a valid certificate being presented and the issue is resolved for addresses. We are still working on implementing a fix for the IPv6 addresses for the Securities public resolvers.

The IPv4 addresses for the Families (1.0.0.3, 1.1.1.3) and the Securities (1.1.1.2, 1.0.0.2) public resolvers via DoH now have a valid certificate being presented and the issue is resolved for those addresses.

We have started working on implementing a fix for the IPv6 addresses for the public resolvers.
The issue has been identified and a fix is being implemented.
We are continuing to investigate this issue.

Cloudflare is aware of, and investigating, an issue with Families and Securities using Cloudflare's public resolvers via DoH and DoT.

Further detail will be provided as more information becomes available.
